Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:10.99,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:46.73,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1023,1)}The Man Named Fanzell
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.53,0:02:08.94,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta was gravely injured due to a curse \Nplaced on him by Vetto of the Third Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:14.88,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The other members of the Black Bulls \Nheaded out to find a cure for his arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:19.86,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle and Finral also visited a \Ncertain man to gain some clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:21.49,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:24.49,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey. I just got out of the bath—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:34.99,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The man that Noelle and Finral came \Nto see is named Fanzell Kruger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.99,0:02:38.88,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this man, and what's \Nhis relationship with Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:42.31,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,To find out, we must look back\Nin time to five months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:44.85,sign_3905_13_5_Months_Ago,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,5 Months Ago
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:48.66,sign_3953_14_A_Village_Out_in,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,743)}A Village Out in the Boonies, Hage
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.32,0:02:47.85,italicstop,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,This story takes place just \Nshortly before Asta and Yuno
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:51.04,italicstop,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,departed for the royal capital to\Ntake the Magic Knights Entrance Exam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:52.81,italicstop,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,after receiving their grimoires.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:59.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta was camping out in a forest \Nnear Hage, training with his sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.18,0:03:10.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:14.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what I'm supposed \Nto do? I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:17.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I never learned how to use a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:22.26,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea how to stand or \Nhold it. Am I practicing right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:26.96,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,O-Out of the way, boy! Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.96,0:03:29.10,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.65,0:03:31.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Jump to the side!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:39.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:43.12,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing. You managed to get \Nrid of it with a single blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:45.96,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I was trying to fish in the river,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:48.79,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,but apparently I was in that boar's territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:51.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:55.38,sign_5557_30_Fanzell_Kruger,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(503,1)}Fanzell Kruger
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:55.38,top,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Fanzell. I'm on a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:57.03,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Fanzell...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.03,0:03:58.29,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me Zell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.29,0:04:00.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm Asta, from Hage Village!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:02.36,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:04.16,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, is that yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:06.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:10.81,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:13.57,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,You're a lifesaver!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:18.13,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had a bite in two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:20.09,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't catch any fish, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:21.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:26.97,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,It's so dry. It's like all the moisture \Nis being sucked out of my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:29.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, why are you naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:32.59,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to get my clothes \Nwet while I was fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:35.35,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:37.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're eating them without \Nknowing what they are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.35,0:04:40.10,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,They're Hage Village's famous tatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:41.75,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Tatoes, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:44.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.72,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:47.97,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:54.94,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what is this? It's really bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:58.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's moguro leaf juice. It's supposed \Nto increase your magical power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:00.65,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I feel much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:04.93,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to thank you. Why don't \Nyou come over to my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:05.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:09.03,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm just staying there \Nwithout permission, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:13.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea a place like \Nthis existed in the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:15.71,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to find an empty house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.47,0:05:19.09,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, one sec. I'll go put some clothes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.61,0:05:26.47,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, a sword that negates magic? \NI've never seen anything like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:31.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna try to pass the Magic Knights \NEntrance Exam with this sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:34.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm camping out \Nin these woods to train!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:35.85,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:38.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:43.03,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Old guy? I'm only 28, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:45.36,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You're 28?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:46.99,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You sure didn't age well!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.23,0:05:50.55,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.05,0:05:56.82,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I'm waiting for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:58.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This deep in the mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:00.86,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,A lot's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:02.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:06.19,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Asta, you're camping out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:08.38,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you stay here \Nwhile you're training?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:10.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That'd help me out a lot, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:13.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're not planning to \Nsteal my tatoes, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:17.11,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,You should treasure your encounters \Nand connections with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.11,0:06:23.19,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,They might go away one day, but they're all \Nexperiences that build up in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:30.22,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance... He's obviously suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:31.91,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Find out more about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:37.72,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll take you up on your offer, Zell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:41.00,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Great. Now, let's decide who \Ngets to chop up the firewood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:43.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:46.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:55.03,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:58.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't working.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:07:01.56,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably because you're not \Ncarrying enough weight on your knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:05.85,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,After you initially swing your sword,\Nyou try to attack again,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:07.40,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not working well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:09.68,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,So you lose your balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:11.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.48,0:07:15.81,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Always make sure your toes are facing the \Nsame direction that your sword is pointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:19.45,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Also, keep your right foot about \Nhalf a step in front of your left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:20.25,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:37.03,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.61,0:07:41.27,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I could! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.61,0:07:41.27,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah... You learned that pretty quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:43.13,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Glad it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:43.16,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:45.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, old guy!\N You know how to use a sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:50.18,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not exactly \Na sword, but... One sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:08:01.05,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Wind Creation Magic: \NEmperor of Slashing Winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:10.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:17.69,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, my magic \Ntakes the shape of a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:20.85,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,The Emperor of Slashing Winds,\N or "Slash" for short.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:23.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're even awesome at naming things!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:27.54,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,So I have some experience\N with swords, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:30.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then please show me how to use a sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:31.71,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:33.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, just a little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:35.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Teach me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:36.78,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:38.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:39.45,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:41.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:42.81,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.81,0:08:44.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:48.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! This is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:50.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Woohoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:53.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! Heck yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:56.31,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,There's just one thing I'd \Nlike you to promise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:55.51,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:09:00.14,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, why do you want to become stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:02.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,To become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:06.12,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:07.65,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:09.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're not gonna laugh at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:10.92,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:13.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Like... say that it's impossible, or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.37,0:09:16.74,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never know if it's \Nimpossible if you don't try.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:19.32,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.01,0:09:22.33,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,that you won't use what I show you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:25.12,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,for anything other than \Nmaking your dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:27.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. What do I need to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:31.80,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Never wrongfully harm others \Nor pick on the weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:34.63,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you don't use it for anything \Nbad like that, I'll teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:37.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even need to tell \Nme not to do stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.19,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:41.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:44.16,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do our best together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:46.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I look forward to training with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:53.98,sign_14194_144_A_Few_Days_Later,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,A Few Days Later
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:03.16,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,You're following up too late \Nwith your left foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:07.16,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to attack consecutively, \Ndon't pause between each slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:08.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.28,0:10:12.21,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Great job, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.81,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing well with both \Nattacking and defending.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:16.72,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Your movements are improving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:19.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're this strong,\N you should've been able to beat
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:22.10,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,that boar on your own no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:25.78,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have my sword or \Ngrimoire with me at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.78,0:10:29.75,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, my swordsmanship \Nisn't that impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:32.36,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,You're just more skilled than you realize.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:36.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure you're \Njust a good teacher, Zell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:41.74,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I used to do something like teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:43.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That explains it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:46.66,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Though my students never took me seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.89,0:10:49.86,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I've taught over a hundred students,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.86,0:10:53.46,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,but you're so talented that you'd \Nprobably be in my top three.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:55.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Top three?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.54,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, maybe top two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.54,0:11:03.00,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Though the top one doesn't really use a sword \Nlike a sword, so that one wouldn't count...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:10.77,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway, I think you'll do just fine, \Neven if you join the Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:12.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:16.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's get right back to training!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:20.25,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on. We're still eating here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:26.08,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A few more days passed, \Nand then she arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:31.21,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late, Instructor Fanzell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:33.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.89,0:11:35.75,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Mariella! Did you find anything out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:37.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Mariella?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.27,0:11:40.14,top,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,She's one of my students.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.27,0:11:42.28,sign_5557_30_Fanzell_Kruger,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(511,788)}Mariella
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:43.55,top,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,She's been helping me look for my fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.23,0:11:47.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Well, what are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:50.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you look for her yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:55.61,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Actually... I can't do anything that'll \Nbring too much attention to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.89,0:12:03.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Asta from Hage Village! This old guy's \Nteaching me how to use my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.94,0:12:04.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:08.80,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you know he's no ordinary man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:12.54,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,I know he looks old, but he seems even older.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:15.93,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are, but he's not
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.05,0:12:14.60,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Old...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:20.51,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,some random old guy that you can \Nlightly address as "old guy."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:22.79,top,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only 28...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:23.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I told you! I'm Asta from Hage Village!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:26.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he is, so why \Ncan't I call him that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:28.68,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,It's a matter of recognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:31.83,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,There's a big difference in the amount \Nof respect you would show him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:34.15,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,knowing just how ancient he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:37.73,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hear an ounce of respect \Nin how you addressed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:41.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How the heck is "old guy" ever \Nsupposed to sound respectful?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:43.01,top,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, could you stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.27,0:12:43.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He's just a random old guy! That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:46.66,top,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you're saying is pretty hurtful, \Nconsidering I'm sitting right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:45.62,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're saying it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:50.24,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, where's Dominante?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:52.68,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Domina?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:56.63,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, Miss Domina...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:59.64,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,may have passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.23,0:13:03.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Dude...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:07.94,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Fanzell explained to Asta what \Nkind of situation he was in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:13.14,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It turned out Fanzell and his fiancée \NDominante belonged to the Diamond army.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.57,0:13:16.83,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The two of them couldn't bear \Nthe army's cruel ways any longer
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:18.26,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and tried to escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:22.51,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,but they were tracked down by \Nsome assassins and got separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:27.62,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Fanzell was supported by his former student,\NMariella, who he let escape earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:29.74,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and she was looking for Dominante.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:33.67,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,If Fanzell made any rash movements, \Nthe assassins would learn of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:36.97,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,so he had no choice but to \Nhide in this house to keep
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.97,0:13:40.50,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Dominante out of danger, \Njust in case she was nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:43.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lot to take in...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:46.40,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,This is Miss Domina's wand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:49.19,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,It was on the ground where you \Nsaid the assassins attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:52.33,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,I also found quite a bit of blood there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:55.10,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:58.35,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, could you leave me alone for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:20.75,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me, Instructor...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.39,0:14:26.95,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Please listen to what I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:33.81,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember when you let me\N and the other students escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:34.81,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:38.31,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:42.06,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,You actually smiled for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.43,0:14:46.57,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see, everyone else died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:47.57,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:54.29,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Assassins sent by the Diamond Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:57.04,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,killed them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:05.21,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:08.19,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Sending the kingdom information
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:12.04,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,as well as eliminating any \Ndefectors is my job now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.63,0:15:16.60,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't cooperate, \NI'd be killed, just like the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:20.73,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I won't kill you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:23.51,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,I was told to bring you back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.93,0:15:27.82,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,This place is completely surrounded, \Nso you won't be able to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:33.02,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,A certain mage warrior has \Nentered his final stages.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.02,0:15:35.27,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they need your advice on
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.27,0:15:38.17,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,the final adjustments he'll \Nneed to function properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.17,0:15:40.89,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,That's where you truly belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:42.79,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:49.30,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,The boy's name is Mars. Stop talking about \Nhim like he's just some kind of weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:53.25,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure. That really doesn't matter to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:56.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You okay, old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:16:00.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And what the hell, Mariella?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:02.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were grateful \Nfor all he did for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:03.81,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:09.04,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I was able to survive because \Nof the fighting techniques he taught me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:10.77,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,so I still respect him greatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:14.41,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I warned you about \Nyour tone when you address him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:16.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then why the heck are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:20.58,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Because if that's all I ever worried about,\N I'd never be able to do my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:24.87,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,So could you please stay out of our way?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:27.88,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to die for some \Nold man you don't know, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:31.03,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I know him pretty damn well now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.03,0:16:34.29,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,No, Asta. Mariella's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.29,0:16:35.39,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,You should run.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:41.84,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,You promised me that you would use \Nwhatever I taught you for your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:46.06,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be wrong to use that here \Nfor some old guy you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:47.56,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:51.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I told you! I know you, old guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:56.45,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I can take care of these \Nguys even if you're not around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:58.20,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But you've been stabbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.73,0:17:03.79,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I promise you I'll get out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:06.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better keep that promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.43,0:17:09.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare die before I see you next!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:10.57,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:15.96,italics,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Asta. You need to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:17.59,italics,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:19.30,italics,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Domina...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:24.81,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.43,0:17:39.54,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:42.17,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what happens to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.61,0:17:44.81,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I've lost the will to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.24,0:17:47.17,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:53.17,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave me alone. I'm tired of all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:57.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:03.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Will to live? A reason to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.65,0:18:07.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you're not supposed \Nto automatically have that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.09,0:18:10.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to find \Nthose things for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:16.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,If you understand, then get\N your ass up and join me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:35.26,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Wind Creation Magic: Emperor of \NSlashing Winds—Winter Wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.25,0:18:38.26,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:44.56,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,That spells sends lots of \NSlashes flying out at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:46.56,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I call it the Flying One.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:48.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What an awesome name!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.24,0:18:51.37,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that pathetic display.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.37,0:18:53.08,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:54.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:55.53,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:59.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My guard's not down at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:01.61,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,He negated my spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.00,0:19:08.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, old guy? You done already?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:12.56,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Only you can decide when you're truly done,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:15.78,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,and you just taught me \Nthat now's not the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:19.56,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let these \Nguys finish me like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.10,0:19:21.30,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Let us retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:24.49,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hold the rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:27.55,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Please make sure to gather the injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:29.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're backing off, just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:34.36,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,To make a surprise attack, you must \Nhave three times the enemy's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:37.57,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose half your men, \Nchange your strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:39.57,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose half of that, then retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:43.07,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,That's what a certain someone taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:46.39,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:49.08,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hunt you down for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:53.29,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on. I'm done running.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:56.13,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,From all of you, as well as myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:58.75,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to be discouraged anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:02.46,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Domina is alive somewhere, I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:06.60,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to search everywhere \Nfor her, so you'd better keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:08.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You hear that, Mariella?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:12.10,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you're ready to have to deal \Nwith his old man stench forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:14.90,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Could you shut up for a bit? \NYou're gonna make an old man cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:17.24,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Please do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:24.91,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Also, your tone has improved. \NDon't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.78,0:20:33.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really going to head out now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.10,0:20:37.58,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm gonna look for \NDomina until I find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:42.15,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm going to try to make up for \Nall the wrongs I did in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.15,0:20:44.79,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't decided exactly how yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:48.04,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,but I need to at least spend \Nthe rest of my life trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:51.21,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,So I won't die that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.21,0:20:54.02,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I've reevaluated my resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.53,0:21:01.90,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if we drag this out any longer, \Nit'll just be harder to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:03.52,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.52,0:21:06.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you seriously leaving,\N just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:10.37,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I am. Time flows differently \Nfor those who try
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:14.27,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,to actually get stuff done \Nand those who don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:17.67,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta save time whenever I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:19.50,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Save time? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.89,0:21:24.87,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,You're also someone who \Ngets stuff done, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.87,0:21:30.31,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Get going, Asta. You already have everything\N you need to get what you want done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:35.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez. {\i1}Now{\i0} you act like a proper mentor?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:38.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, old guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.06,0:21:40.02,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better become the Wizard King, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.63,0:21:43.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I guess I should \Nget back to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.26,0:21:54.04,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Asta! This is your final lesson!\N Defeat this boar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.40,0:21:56.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Do it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.18,0:21:59.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Also, why are you naked again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.53,0:22:01.89,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.89,0:22:05.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't come this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.70,0:23:41.56,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Domina, where are you, my love?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.56,0:23:43.67,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.67,0:23:47.11,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, miss! I'd like to ask you a \Nquestion. Wait, don't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.49,0:23:51.25,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 56:\N"The Man Named Fanzell Continued."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.32,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 56\N\N{\fs18} The Man Named Fanzell Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.25,0:23:53.82,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let it bother you that I'm naked!
